name: Erstellung
description: Datum, wann die Quelle geschaffen wurde

name: creation
description: date identifies when the resource was brought into existence

name: Publikation
description: Dateum, wann die Quelle publiziert wurde

name: publication
description: date identifies when the resource was issued

name: letzte Änderung
description: Datum, wann eine Revision durchgeführt wurde

name: revision
description: date identifies when the resource was examined or re-examined and improved or amended

name: Datenverantwortung
description: Verantworlicher für die Datenquelle und deren Pflege

name: Custodian
description: Party that accepts accountability and responsibility for the data and ensures appropriate care and maintenance of the resource

name: Auskunft
description: Kontaktperson, die Informationen über die Datenqulle geben kann

name: Point of Contact
description: Party who can be contacted for acquiring knowledge about or acquisition of the resource

name: Datenerfassung
description: Verantworlicher für die Zusammenstellung der Informationen und Durchführung von Forschung

name: Principal Investigator
description: Key party responsible for gathering information and conducting research

name: Auswertung
description: Bearbeiter der Daten in einer Art, dass die Quelle modifiziert wurde.

name: Processor
description: Party who has processed the data in a manner such that the resource has been modified

name: ucs2
description: 16-bit fixierte Größe Universal Character Set, basierend auf ISO/IEC 10646

name: ucs2
description: 16-bit fixed size Universal Character Set, based on ISO/IEC 10646

name: ucs4
description: 32-bit fixierte Größe Universal Character Set, basierend auf ISO/IEC 10646

name: ucs4
description: 32-bit fixed size Universal Character Set, based on ISO/IEC 10646

name: utf7
description: 7-bit variable Größe UCS Transfer Format, basierend auf ISO/IEC 10646

name: utf7
description: 7-bit variable size UCS Transfer Format, based on ISO/IEC 10646

name: utf8
description: 8-bit variable Größe UCS Transfer Format, basierend auf ISO/IEC 10646

name: utf8
description: 8-bit variable size UCS Transfer Format, based on ISO/IEC 10646

name: utf16
description: 16-bit variable Größe UCS Transfer Format, basierend auf ISO/IEC 10646

name: utf16
description: 16-bit variable size UCS Transfer Format, based on ISO/IEC 10646

name: Jis
description: japanese code set used for electronic transmission

name: ShiftJIS
description: japanese code set used on MS-DOS based machines

name: EucJP
description: japanese code set used on UNIX based machines

name: UsAscii
description: united states ASCII code set (ISO 646 US)

name: Komplex
description: Satz geometrischer Primitiver, wobei deren Grenzen durch ein Zusammenschluss anderer Primitiver gebildet werden können

name: complexes
description: set of geometric primitives such that their boundaries can be represented as a union of other primitives

name: Verbund
description: verbundener Satz von Kurven, Körpern oder Oberflächen

name: composites
description: connected set of curves, solids or surfaces

name: Kurve
description: beschränkte, 1-D geometrische Primitive, die ein continuierliches Bild einer Linie darstellt

name: curve
description: bounded, 1-dimensional geometric primitive, representing the continuous image of a line

name: Punkt
description: 0-D geometrische Primitive, welche eine Position beschreibt ohne eine Ausdehnung zu haben

name: point
description: zero-dimensional geometric primitive, representing a position but not having an extent

name: Körper
description: begrenzte, verbundene 3-D geometrische Primitive, welche ein kontinuierliches Bild eines Raumes beschreibt

name: solid
description: bounded, connected 3-dimensional geometric primitive, representing the continuous image of a region of space

name: Oberfläche
description: begrenzte, verbundene 2-D geometrische Primitive, welche ein kontinuierliches Bild einer Ebene oder Region beschreibt

name: surface
description: bounded, connected 2-dimensional geometric, representing the continuous image of a region of a plane

name: Wissenszweig
description: Zweig einer Ausbildung oder spezialisierten Lernens

name: Discipline
description: keyword identifies a branch of instruction or specialized learning

name: Stratum
description: keyword identifies the layer(s) of any deposited substance

name: Zeitraum
description: Zeitraum in Bezug auf den Datensatz

name: Temporal
description: keyword identifies a time period related to the dataset

name: Theme
description: keyword identifies a particular subject or topic

name: continual
description: data is repeatedly and frequently updated

name: weekly
description: Ddata is updated on a weekly basis

name: fortnightly
description: Data is updated every two weeks

name: quarterly
description: Data is updated every three months

name: biannually
description: Data is updated twice each year

name: as Needed
description: Data is updated as deemed necessary

name: irregular
description: Data is updated in intervals that are uneven in duration

name: notPlanned
description: There are no plans to update the data

name: unknown
description: Frequency of maintenance for the data is not known

name: completed
description: production of the data has been completed

name: archiviert
description: Die Daten sind in einem Archiv abgelegt

name: historicalArchive
description: Data has been stored in an offline storage facility

name: obsolet
description: Die Daten sind nicht mehr länger relevant

name: geplant
description: Ein Zeitpunkt wurde festgelegt, an dem die Daten kreiert werden

name: planned
description: fixed date has been established upon or by which the data will be created or updated

name: benötigt
description: Die Daten müssen generiert bzw. erneuert werden

name: required
description: Data needs to be generated or updated

name: under development
description: Data is currently in the process of being created

name: Vektor
description: Geographische Daten werden mittels Verktordaten präsentiert

name: vector
description: vector data is used to represent geographic data

name: Rasterdaten
description: Geographische Daten werden mittels Rasterdaten dargestellt

name: grid
description: grid data is used to represent geographic data

name: Texttabelle
description: Geographische Daten werden mittels Texttabellen dargestellt

name: textTable
description: textual or tabular data is used to represent geographic data

name: TIN
description: Geographische Daten werden mittels eines trinangulären irregulären Netzes dargestellt dargestellt

name: Stereomodell
description: Geographische Daten werden mittels eines stereosehenden Models dargestellt

name: stereoModel
description: three-dimensional view formed by the intersecting homologous rays of an overlapping pair of images

name: Video
description: Geographische Daten werden mittels einer Videoaufnahme dargestellt

name: Farming
description: rearing of animals and/or cultivation of plants

name: Flora, Fauna, Habitate
description: Flora und Fauna in der natürlichen Umwelt

name: Biota
description: flora and/or fauna in natural environment. Examples: wildlife, vegetation, biological sciences, ecology, wilderness, sealife, wetlands, habitat

name: Grenzen
description: Rechtl. Beschreibungen und Grenzen von Land

name: Boundaries
description: legal land descriptions. Examples: political and administrative boundaries

name: Climatology MeteorologyAtmosphere
description: processes and phenomena of the atmosphere. Examples: cloud cover, weather, climate, atmospheric conditions, climate change, precipitation

name: Economy
description: economic activities, conditions and employment. Examples: production, labour, revenue, commerce, industry, tourism and ecotourism, forestry, fisheries, commercial or subsistence hunting, etc.

name: Elevation
description: height above or below sea level. Examples: altitude, bathymetry, digital elevation models, slope, derived products

name: Environment
description: environmental resources, protection and conservation. Examples: environmental pollution, waste storage and treatment, environmental impact assessment, monitoring environmental risk, nature reserves, landscape

name: Geoscientific Information
description: information pertaining to earth sciences. Examples: geophysical features and processes, geology, minerals, sciences dealing with the composition, structure and origin of the earth’s rocks, risks of earthquakes

name: Health
description: health, health services, human ecology, and safety. Examples: disease and illness, factors affecting health, hygiene, substance abuse, mental and physical health, health services

name: Imagery Base Maps EarthCover
description: base maps. Examples: land cover, topographic maps, imagery, unclassified images, annotations

name: Intelligence Military
description: military bases, structures, activities. Examples: barracks, training grounds, military transportation, information

name: Binnengewässer
description: Inlandwasser, Abflüsse und deren Eigenschaften und Charakteristika

name: Inland Waters
description: inland water features, drainage systems and their characteristics. Examples: rivers and glaciers, salt lakes, water utilization plans, dams, currents, floods, water quality, hydrographic charts

name: Location
description: positional information and services. Examples: addresses, geodetic networks, control points, postal zones and services, place names

name: Ozeane
description: Ozeane und deren Charakteristika und Eigenschaften

name: Oceans
description: features and characteristics of salt water bodies (excluding inland waters): Examples: tides, tidal waves, coastal information, reefs

name: Kataster
description: Informationen zu angemessenem Handeln für die zukünftige Nutzung des Landes

name: PlanningCadastre
description: information used for appropriate actions for future use of the land Examples: land use maps, zoning maps, cadastral surveys, land ownership

name: Society
description: characteristics of society and cultures. Examples: settlements, anthropology, archaeology, education, traditionalbeliefs, manners and customs, demographic data, recreational areas and activities,

name: Structure
description: man-made construction. Examples: buildings, museums, churches, factories, housing, monuments, shops, towers

name: Transport
description: Hilfsmittel und Geräte zum Befördern von Personen und/oder Gütern

name: Transportation
description: means and aids for conveying persons and/or goods. Examples: roads, airports/airstrips, shipping routes, tunnels, nautical charts, vehicle or vessel location, aeronautical charts, railways

name: Energie und Kommunikation
description: Energie-, Wasser- und Abfallsysteme sowie Kommunikationsinfrastruktur und Services.

name: Utilities Communication
description: energy, water and waste systems and communications infrastructure and services. Examples: hydroelectricity, geothermal, solar and nuclear sources of energy, water purification and distribution, sewage collection and disposal, etc.

name: geometrisch
description: Geometrisch Objekte ohn jegliche Struktur, die die Topologie beschreibt

name: geometryOnly
description: geometry objects without any additional structure which describes topology

name: Planar (1D)
description: 1-dimensionaler topologischer Komplex, der eine Fläche ist

name: Planar (2D)
description: 2-dimensionaler topologischer Komplex, der eine Fläche ist

name: Oberflächengraph (1D)
description: 1-dimensionaler topologischer Komplex, der isomorph zu einer Untermenge einer Oberfläche ist

name: surfaceGraph
description: 1-dimensional topological complex which is isomorphic to a subset of a surface

name: Oberfläche(2D)
description: 2-dimensionaler topologischer Komplex, der isomorph zu einer Untermenge einer Oberfläche ist

name: fullSurfaceGraph
description: 2-dimensional topological complex which is isomorphic to a subset of a surface

name: fullTopology3D
description: complete coverage of a 3D coordinate space

name: Abstrakte Topologie
description: Topologischer Komplex ohne jegliche spezifische geometrische Realisierung

name: abstract
description: topological complex without any specified geometric realization
